short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension that help user transfer gitlab milestone to gantt chart

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The plugin will generate a gantt chart automatically in Gitlab Milestone page.
The start date should be described in each milestone issue description with format: /start_date YYYY/MM/DD.
The end date will each milestone issue's due date.

Go to https://gitlab.com/k402xxxcenxxx/milestone-gantt-chart-demo/-/milestones to see the demo.
